title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in table inside a grid cell
OB: When attempting to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data in the table inside the grid cell should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR: 1. Insert a table into one grid cell. 2. Insert another table into another grid cell. 3. Attempt to export the data in the tables within the grid cells.
